name: ZARA RED SPARKLE NAIL WRAPS - Gel Nails Effect
description:
Gel nail stickers for a premium and easy at-home manicure.

Instructions for use:
Wash hands with soap and then dry to ensure proper product adherence.
Apply the nail stickers.
File down excess product so they fit the shape of your nails.

Removal instructions: With the wooden stick, peel off the gel strip starting at the edge and peeling towards the center of the nail.

name: RADIANCE DROPS PRIMER
description:
This illuminating base, light like a serum, will provide glow and luminosity to your skin.
Customize your glow with four application options:
1. Use it as a stand-alone product to illuminate your skin.
2. Apply before your make-up foundation.
3. Blend it with your make-up foundation. 
4. Apply it on top of your make-up foundation to illuminate highlights on your face.

name: METALLIC EYE SHADOW

name: ZARA VELVET PINCH MATTE LIP BALM

name: BLACK TUBING EYELASH MASCARA - FOOLPROOF DAILY
description:
A daily use mascara that lengthens and lifts lashes without build-up. The precision brush allows for easy and uniform application. 

A striking look thanks to its innovative TUBING formula that gives your eyelashes: 
- Lengthening effect
- Lifting effect
- Resistant to water
- No flaking
- Does not clump the eyelashes
- It is easily removed by simply applying warm water to the eyelashes and wiping with a finger or cotton swab.

name: Cream blush - ZARA FIRST FLUSH CREAM BLUSH
description:
New ultra-sensorial cream blush that turns into powder on contact with the skin. Its lightweight texture melts into the skin, leaving a natural and luminous finish.
It can be applied directly with your fingertips for greater intensity or with a brush for lighter coverage.
Formulated to enhance the cheeks leaving a radiant, rosy, and luminous finish.

name: ZARA FIRST FLUSH LIQUID BLUSH

LIQUID BLUSH An intensely pigmented liquid blush that goes on easily for a flawless, glowing complexion.

Illuminating your complexion with radiant tones, the formula blends beautifully for natural radiance while providing a stunning natural skin look.

name: Cream bronzing powder - ZARA CREAM BRONZER
description:
New cream bronzer. Its ultra-sensorial, lightweight texture transforms into powder on contact with the skin for a naturally luminous and pleasant finish. This formula allows you to create a natural tan or more pronounced contours, depending on the desired effect.
 
It can be applied directly with your fingertips for greater intensity or with a brush for lighter coverage.

Try different shades to achieve the desired effect. For subtle contours, choose a light shade and for a more striking effect, a more saturated shade.
